{"tid":2340773,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解呢個世界既人會阻止人自殺？","createTime":"2020-12-25T18:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T12:37:43.000Z","uid":331286,"like":64,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ce936e633124a303d67f887f5743bd59ed07db43","tid":2340773,"uid":331286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:31:03.000Z","msg":"一直都唔明<br />\n<br />\n物競天擇<br />\n唔係就係適者生存咩<br />\n<br />\n咁點解適應唔到呢個世界既人<br />\n唔俾佢死<br />\n<br />\n仲要宗教方便又講到自殺者落地獄<br />\n防止自殺又講到要珍惜生命<br />\n然後又一推邊個邊個會唔捨得你<br />\n身邊既人會好痛苦bala bala<br />\n<br />\n但有無諗過適應唔到個世界仲痛苦<br />\n要說服到自己真係overcome到<br />\n<br />\n但自己個世界已經穿晒窿<br />\n邊個真係知個種感受<br />\n<br />\n唔緊 最緊要你自殺不成功"},{"pid":"a982f330159f870958c502e26220122652d250cb","tid":2340773,"uid":331286,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:32:12.000Z","msg":"真係諗唔透防止自殺呢個諗法"},{"pid":"c0f19df676156e068cbac808717cdc41bb648917","tid":2340773,"uid":140738,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:32:19.000Z","msg":"因為要洗地"},{"pid":"358cfeeb561f27b3f9d10983d896202ff3b11f93","tid":2340773,"uid":267808,"like":7,"dislike":10,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:33:06.000Z","msg":"呢一刻唔適應 唔代表之後都係<br />\n<br />\n好多人都係一時衝動 <br />\n<br />\n社會更加冇可能鼓勵做呢樣嘢"},{"pid":"40df0c2c3a853f409099cf4b2917b26276c1d1b8","tid":2340773,"uid":267808,"like":33,"dislike":3,"score":30,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:33:56.000Z","msg":"講真你真係想死 邊個阻到你"},{"pid":"eaea84fb24f4008f0f7016f0d65890fd92c120c8","tid":2340773,"uid":124976,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:34:10.000Z","msg":"因為你都要同我一齊承受痛苦"},{"pid":"070ccb49164004ce4a09f9a354dfd282e2691596","tid":2340773,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:34:41.000Z","msg":"因為同情心係人類進化失誤"},{"pid":"c3bd8acb295bfb6c89eb1e7475c055caab184bab","tid":2340773,"uid":325346,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T18:34:47.000Z","msg":"因為人有偽善的一